did.head: Overview
did.unittitle: Georg Kreisel correspondence with Jean van Heijenoort
did.abstract: Correspondence, notes, memoranda, articles and other materials by Professor Georg Kreisel, sent to his colleague, Professor J. van Heijenoort of Harvard University. Includes some correspondence with other colleagues.

scopecontent.head: Description of the Collection
scopecontent.p: Correspondence, notes, memoranda, articles and other materials by Professor Georg Kreisel, sent to his colleague, Professor J. van Heijenoort of Harvard University. Includes some correspondence with other colleagues.
